                    <callout1>2. LAMP MONITOR</callout1>
                    <callout1>3. LAMP POWER SUPPLY</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <para>The
                <hotlnk xrefid="f082901180">lamp monitor</hotlnk>
                can be found at the front of the bus above the dashboard.
            </para>
            <para>The lamp monitor system allows the driver to see if any lamps connected to the monitor are not
                functioning properly without having to exit the vehicle.
            </para>
